'''雷西姆农城堡''' ({{lang-el|Φορτέτζα}},[[意大利语|意大利语]]：Fortezza；英语：Fortezza of Rethymno) 是[[希腊|希腊]][[克里特岛|克里特岛]][[雷西姆农|雷西姆农]]的一座城堡，由[[威尼斯共和国|威尼斯共和国]]建于16世纪，保存完好，并向公众开放。

雷西姆农城堡为不规则平面，周长1307米，周边有圣尼古拉<ref>{{cite web|title=The Building at the St. Nicolas Bastion|url=http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/saint-nicolas/saint-nicolas-building.html|website=tour.rethymno.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016150200/http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/saint-nicolas/saint-nicolas-building.html|archivedate=16 October 2015}}</ref>、圣保罗<ref>{{cite web|title=Fortezza, the Santa Maria Bastion|url=http://www.explorecrete.com/crete-west/Rethymnon_Fortezza/Fortezza_1300_bastion.html|website=Explore Crete|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140218235033/http://www.explorecrete.com/crete-west/Rethymnon_Fortezza/Fortezza_1300_bastion.html|archivedate=18 February 2014}}</ref>、圣以利亚<ref>{{cite web|title=The 'Erofyli' Theatre|url=http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/theater-erofili/erofili.html|website=tour.rethymno.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016144550/http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/theater-erofili/erofili.html|archivedate=16 October 2015}}</ref>、圣路加<ref>{{cite web|title=The Bastion of St. Lucas|url=http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/saint-lukas/saint-loukas.html|website=tour.rethymno.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016144839/http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/saint-lukas/saint-loukas.html|archivedate=16 October 2015}}</ref>四座堡垒。

城堡内有数座建筑。苏丹易卜拉欣清真寺，原为圣尼古拉主教座堂<ref>{{cite web|title=The Mosque of Ibrahim Han|url=http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/tzami-chan/tzami-chan.html|website=tour.rethymno.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016150609/http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/tzami-chan/tzami-chan.html|archivedate=16 October 2015}}</ref>。附近的一座建筑，原为主教府<ref>{{cite web|title=Episcope Palace|url=http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/bishop-residence/bishop-residence.html|website=tour.rethymno.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016150929/http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/bishop-residence/bishop-residence.html|archivedate=16 October 2015}}</ref>。此外还有一些教会建筑<ref>{{cite web|title=Holy Temple of St. Theodore of Trihinas|url=http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/saint-theodor/trichinas.html|website=tour.rethymno.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016151658/http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/saint-theodor/trichinas.html|archivedate=16 October 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Fortezza, the church of Agia Ekaterini|url=http://www.explorecrete.com/crete-west/Rethymnon_Fortezza/Fortezza_1800_agiaaikaterini.html|website=Explore Crete|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204022735/http://www.explorecrete.com/crete-west/Rethymnon_Fortezza/Fortezza_1800_agiaaikaterini.html|archivedate=4 February 2014}}</ref>。

==历史==
城堡位于旧城堡山（''Paleokastro''）上，古希腊卫城的原址<ref name=tour>{{cite web|title=The Fortezza fortress|url=http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/fortezza/fortezza.html|website=tour.rethymno.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151016143821/http://tour.rethymno.gr/en/route4/fortezza/fortezza.html|archivedate=2015-10-16}}</ref>。在10-13世纪，[[拜占庭帝国|拜占庭帝国]]在其东侧建造城堡''Castrum Rethemi''。[[威尼斯共和国|威尼斯共和国]]占领后，名为旧城堡（''Castel Vecchio''或''Antico Castello''）<ref name=explorecrete>{{cite web|last1=Kivernitaki|first1=Maria|last2=Samatas|first2=Yannis|title=Fortezza in Rethymnon|url=http://www.explorecrete.com/crete-west/Rethymnon_Fortezza.html|website=Explore Crete|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150401004336/http://www.explorecrete.com/crete-west/Rethymnon_Fortezza.html|archivedate=1 April 2015}}</ref>。威尼斯统治时期，雷西姆农成为克里特岛第三大城市。1540-1570年，沿海修建了城墙，但仍未能抵御1571年的入侵<ref name=explorecrete/>。

1571年奥斯曼帝国征服[[塞浦路斯|塞浦路斯]]以后，克里特岛成为威尼斯最大的海外据点。威尼斯在雷西姆农山上修建了新城堡，保护城市和港口。工程开始于1573年9月13日，完成于1580年。城堡内设有威尼斯人的行政机构.仅在奥斯曼军队入侵时收容避难的居民。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Valia|first1=Angelaki|title=Fortezza Castle|url=http://odysseus.culture.gr/h/3/gh351.jsp?obj_id=15421|website=Ministry of Culture and Sport|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130326121547/http://odysseus.culture.gr/h/3/gh351.jsp?obj_id=15421|archivedate=26 March 2013|language=el|date=2012}}</ref>

1646年9月29日，奥斯曼军队包围了雷西姆农。11月13日，威尼斯人向奥斯曼军队投降<ref>{{cite web|title=Die Belagerung von Rethymno|url=http://www.rethymnon.gr/index.php?id=122,537,0,0,1,0|website=rethymnon.gr|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605034601/http://www.rethymnon.gr/index.php?id=122,537,0,0,1,0|archivedate=5 June 2009|language=de}}</ref>。到20世纪初，城堡内已经建起许多房屋。这些房屋在二战以后被拆除，城堡内只留下少数历史建筑。
